title: Waterfront 2 Bedroom | Modern Kitchen | W/D
posting_body: ['If you are interested in this two-bedroom waterfront on Lake Mallalieu request a tour so our friendly guest service team may help you.', 'Visit', 'stpaulrental com', 'and click', 'REQUEST A TOUR', '.', 'For everything else contact our friendly for guidance with our top-tier homes in prime locations at', 'show contact info', 'or', 'help <at> stpaulrental com', 'This beautiful 2-bedroom is on Lake Mallalieu and the St. Croix River in Hudson, WI.', 'Home is surrounded by breathtaking water views and epic beaches, including Hudson Pier Beach and a chain of beach islands near Swing Bridge Island and Can Island.', 'Well-equipped with a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, microwave, washer/dryer, deck, AC, fenced yard, and more.', 'Near Hwy 94 for quick access to St Paul.', 'Two bedrooms, one bathroom, attached garage.', 'Utilities, taxes, and trash costs are based upon actual usage.', 'The lease is 12+ months.', 'The first Little Free Library (a library based on the honor system) is located next to this home.', 'This home is available for move-in with good credit.', 'Visit stpaulrental com and click REQUEST A TOUR when you’re ready to view this breathtaking waterfront home surrounded by beautiful beaches.', 'Our friendly team answers questions sent with completed tour requests.', 'For everything else, contact our friendly guest service team for help finding a top-tier home in a prime location', 'show contact info', 'or help @ stpaulrental com']
